Name: jp2a
Version: 1.3.0
Release: alt1

Summary: an utility for converting JPEG images to ASCII
Summary(ru_RU.UTF-8): утилита для конвертации изображений JPEG в ASCII art

License: %gpl2only
Group: Text tools
URL: https://github.com/Talinx/jp2a
#URL: https://github.com/cslarsen/jp2a
